  "description": {
    "zh": "我们的瑞典朋友们似乎在他们对塔科夫救援行动进行\"审计\"时弄丢了一块硬盘。去街区上他们遗弃的装甲车里把它取回来。那块硬盘里有些有趣的东西：避税天堂、禁运技术交易、货运清单……把它交给我，我们或许能推动斯德哥尔摩把一些联合国援助预算转到我们这边来。要是他们与TerraGroup的那些肮脏交易被曝光，岂不是很可惜？",
    "en": "Our Swedish pals seem to have lost a hard drive during their little \"audit\" of Tarkov’s relief operations. Go fetch it from their abandoned armored vehicle out in the Streets. That drive’s got some juicy details: tax havens, embargoed tech deals, shipping manifests... Get it to me and we could nudge Stockholm into redirecting some UN aid budgets our way. Wouldn’t it be a pity if their shady deals with TerraGroup got out?"
  },
